@startuml
title <font size=10>Record Aktivitas - Owner</font>

actor Owner
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "Database" as DB
participant "View" as View

Owner -> Browser: Akses halaman Record Aktivitas
Browser -> Controller: GET /pemilik/record-aktivitas
Controller -> DB: Query RecordAktivitas with filters
Note over DB: Filter: user, action, date range, search

DB --> Controller: Return filtered activities
Controller -> DB: Query distinct actions (untuk dropdown)
Controller -> DB: Query users role=0 (untuk dropdown)

DB --> Controller: Return actions & users list
Controller -> View: Pass data (recordAktivitas, actions, users)
View --> Browser: Render activity log table with filters

Owner -> Browser: Apply filter (user/action/date/search)
Browser -> Controller: GET dengan parameters filter
Controller -> DB: Query dengan filter terbaru
DB --> Controller: Return filtered results (paginate 50)
Controller -> View: Pass filtered data
View --> Browser: Update tabel dengan hasil filter

Owner -> Browser: Klik halaman next (pagination)
Browser -> Controller: GET dengan page parameter
Controller -> DB: Query page berikutnya
DB --> Controller: Return data halaman berikutnya
View --> Browser: Tampilkan halaman berikutnya

@enduml
